
slais.sh

As root (or via sudo) type:

sh slais.sh 2>&1 | tee /tmp/slais.log


FAQ

Where Squid installed?
- /opt/squid

Where is the config file?
- /opt/squid/etc/squid.conf

How launch/status/stop Squid?
- service squid.slais start
- service squid.slais status
- service squid.slais stop

Where is the file with passwords?
- /opt/squid/etc/passwd
- Owner nobody, group nogroup

How add a new users?
- htpasswd /opt/squid/etc/passwd <username>

Standard-Port
- 3128
